plot: An accident lands Jaye's dad in the hospital; meanwhile, Jayes' 6-1/2-year high-school reunion is held in town and she is asked to help.

After Jaye accidentally gets her father run over by a car, the muses coerce her into helping a despised former classmate plan their high school's 6-1/2-year reunion--which she wasn't even planning to attend. She tries to do as little as possible, but gets thrust into her golden-girl classmate's life.—AJMMMC
